                    simple manner. Our design uses a modern sans-serif font type, button and component design, as well as layouts to make the user interface and 
                    experience a lot more enjoyable and fun to interact with especially in our search page.
                </p>

                <h6 class="page-row-subtitle fw-600 text-charcoal m-t-50 m-b-20">Mobile friendly approach</h6>

