                    shouldn’t be limited by their devices to enjoy a clean user interface and search function. With Bootstrap’s tailor made grid and layout system, 
                    we’ve developed findDining to be a mobile friendly and responsive web application that will update and resize its design on the fly depending 
                    on what device someone is using to view and interact with our web app. 
                </p>

                <h6 class="page-row-subtitle fw-600 text-charcoal m-t-50 m-b-20">Constant updates</h6>

